translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_15cc2c77:

    # t "No, Koyama. The fact of the matter is that a significant number of female students have expressed safety concerns surrounding your continued presence in this school."
    t "No, Koyama. Lo cierto es que un número significativo de alumnas han expresado preocupación por su seguridad alrededor de tu contina presencia en esta escuela."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:749
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_31e1f545:

    # t "And do not expect me to overlook your continued harassment of Homura and Akemi."
    t "Y no esperes que pase por alto tu continuo acoso hacia Homura y Akemi."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:750
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f2593070:

    # "My back stiffens at the sudden mention of those two. But what the fuck?"
    "Mi espalda se pone rígida con la súbita mención de esas dos. Pero ¿qué mierda?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:751
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0ac6f1ad:

    # ks surprised "{cps=20}Hiroko and Nozomi? B-but I didn't-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ks surprised "{cps=20}¿Hiroko y Nozomi? P-pero no les-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:752
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5b1c40e6:

    # t "Multiple witnesses observed you approaching your former classmates on the rooftop last Friday."
    t "Múltiples testigos te observaron acercándote a tus excompañeras en la azotea el viernes pasado."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:753
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bcab499e:

    # "Friday? On the rooftop? But..."
    "¿Viernes? ¿En la azotea? Pero..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:754
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3ba686ce:

    # ks "I was apologizing!"
    ks "¡Me estaba disculpando!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:755
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a63185cc:

    # t "Frankly, I don't care what you thought you were doing. The impact of your actions has been understood."
    t "Francamente, no me importa lo que creyeras que hacías. El impacto de tus acciones ha quedado claro."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:756
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_eb639d3b:

    # t "So, what I have to say next does not bring me pleasure. But you have left me no choice."
    t "Así que, lo que diré a continuación no me complace. Pero no me dejas otra opción."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:757
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_eff5474d:

    # "His expression becomes a little more severe as he leans forward against his desk, and I brace myself for the worst."
    "Su expresión se vuelve un poco más severa al inclinarse hacia adelante, y yo me preparo para lo peor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:758
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_48e3cfc8:

    # t "You are hereby suspended, effective immediately."
    t "Por la presente quedas suspendido, con efecto inmediato."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:759
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7a75e5b1:

    # "And there it is."
    "Y ahí está."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:760
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_79c6c8fa:

    # ks "{cps=15}But Sir-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=15}Pero, Señor-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:761
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b685e289:

    # t "As the mock examinations are tomorrow you will be permitted to take them here, but you are to be on the school premises for no other purpose."
    t "Dado que los exámenes simulacro serán mañana, te será permitido tomarlos aquí, pero no has de presentarte en las instalaciones de la escuela por ninguna otra razón."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:762
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_644865a0:

    # t "Are we clear, Koyama?"
    t "¿Quedó claro, Koyama?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:763
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4441f9b7:

    # ks neutral "... Yes, Sir."
    ks neutral "... Sí, Señor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:764
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9ce152d8:

    # t "Good. Mr. Kobayashi has already been informed of my decision. Get your things and leave."
    t "Bien. El profesor Kobayashi ya fue informado de mi decisión. Ve por tus cosas y retírate."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:767
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b31cae9e:

    # "I knew this was coming, but even so..."
    "Sabía que esto vendría, pero aun así..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:768
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_465a8769:

    # "For it to happen like this..."
    "Que ocurra de esta forma..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:770
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ba6b3622:

    # "To be ejected so quickly. Discarded like yesterday's trash."
    "Ser echado tan rápidamente. Botado como basura de ayer."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:771
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b40dfa0c:

    # "And to be so HUMILIATED!"
    "¡Y ser tan HUMILLADO!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:772
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2b6bbe12:

    # "They're forcing me to go back in that classroom, get my stuff and leave in front of everybody in the middle of the day."
    "Me obligan a volver a ese salón, tomar mis cosas y marcharme delante de todo el mundo en pleno día."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:773
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9190ed2d:

    # "It's... it's unbearable."
    "Es... es insoportable."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:774
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4e333a9c:

    # "I'll never be able to show my face in there again..."
    "Nunca podré volver a mostrar mi cara ahí..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:797
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_87ad0617:

    # "... Huh? Was that who I think it was?"
    "... ¿Eh? ¿Esa de ahí era Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:798
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_88b77dc7:

    # "Walking past the door to class 3-C, I head quietly towards the toilets our student council president just disappeared into."
    "Pasando de largo la puerta del salón 3-C, camino silenciosamente hacia los baños a los que la presidenta de nuestro consejo estudiantil acaba de entrar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:800
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ae60417e:

    # "It hasn't even been an hour since the end of lunch. I guess 'Kiko was too busy saving face with her student council buddies to see to her needs."
    "No ha pasado ni una hora desde el almuerzo. Supongo que 'Kiko estaba muy ocupada salvando su reputación con sus amigos del consejo para atender sus necesidades."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:801
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0ce41098:

    # "Too busy selling me out to the school faculty... yeah, that's it, isn't it."
    "Muy ocupada vendiéndome a la facultad... sí, eso fue, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:802
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e47f44dc:

    # "It can't have been a coincidence that she entered the classroom with Mr. Kobayashi. They talked. She may have even had an audience with the principal."
    "No pudo ser una coincidencia que entrara al salón con el profesor Kobayashi. Hablaron. Tal vez hasta tuvo una audiencia con el director."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:803
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6151d741:

    # "That's why he decided to act on me now. The word of our student council president would've been decisive."
    "Por eso decidió actuar contra mí ahora. La palabra de la presidenta de nuestro consejo estudiantil habría sido decisiva."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:804
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_48144252:

    # "I can't begrudge Akiko for being afraid of me, not after what happened with Hiroko but still, she didn't just abandon me."
    "No puedo culpar a Akiko por tenerme miedo, no después de lo que pasó con Hiroko, pero aun así, no solo me abandonó."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:807
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_343a86e4:

    # "She betrayed me..."
    "Me traicionó..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:818
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d1cca3bc:

    # "But it seems fate has given me another chance to right my world."
    "Pero parece que el destino me ha dado otra oportunidad de enderezar mi mundo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:819
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_71047e4a:

    # "I'm a creepy, manipulative monster. I know it, she knows it, everyone knows it."
    "Soy un horrendo monstruo manipulador. Yo lo sé, ella lo sabe, todos lo saben."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:820
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_be2cd6c0:

    # "Why not embrace who I am? Why don't I just take what I want?"
    "¿Por qué no aceptar quién soy? ¿Por qué no simplemente tomo lo que quiero?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:826
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cc63c9d5:

    # "Because I'm seriously thinking about brainwashing a girl on purpose in a school toilet?"
    "Porque ¿en serio estoy pensando lavarle el cerebro a una chica a propósito en un baño escolar?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:827
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6454077c:

    # a "Hm? Is someone there?"
    a "¿Mm? ¿Hay alguien ahí?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:829
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8b4cc670:

    # "I quickly step outside as I realized I just gasped at my own monstrousness."
    "Salgo rápidamente, soltando un grito ahogado ante mi propia monstruosidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:830
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_49765e38:

    # "Fuck. What am I doing? What am I THINKING?!"
    "Carajo. ¿Qué estoy haciendo? ¡¿Qué estoy PENSANDO?!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:831
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8cb06cfe:

    # "I know it's too late to save my school career. Too late to save my immediate future..."
    "Sé que es muy tarde para salvar mi carrera escolar. Muy tarde para salvar mi futuro inmediato..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:832
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c0440e9c:

    # "... But is it really too late to save myself?"
    "... Pero ¿será muy tarde para salvarme a mí?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:837
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0d243c65:

    # ks smirk "{size=16}\"Save myself\"?{/size}"
    ks smirk "{size=16}¿\"Salvarme a mí\"?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:838
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e2be70c6:

    # "I scoff quietly at the absurdity of such a thought. What the fuck does that even mean now?"
    "Me río en voz baja de lo absurdo de tal idea. ¿Eso qué mierda significa ahora?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:839
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bbbddf55:

    # "No amount of apologizing is going to stop people thinking I'm the devil incarnate."
    "Ni todas las disculpas del mundo harán que la gente deje de pensar que soy el demonio encarnado."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:840
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_19499613:

    # "It doesn't matter how much I try to move on and make better decisions; my actions last week will define me in the eyes of everyone I meet."
    "No importa cuánto intente seguir adelante y tomar mejores decisiones; mis acciones de la semana pasada me definirán a los ojos de todo aquel que me encuentre."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:841
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4692f6ae:

    # "I'll never be able to forget. And they'll never be able to forgive."
    "Nunca podré olvidar. Y nunca podrán perdonar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:842
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_267e8f1b:

    # "So why fight it?"
    "Así que, ¿por qué luchar?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:849
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ccc12789:

    # "Why not be selfish?"
    "¿Por qué no ser egoísta?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:853
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_65dbaf69:

    # "Why not sneak over to Akiko's cubicle and launch the spiral app on my phone while waiting for her to come out?"
    "¿Por qué no escabullirme hasta el cubículo de Akiko y abrir la aplicación de espiral en mi teléfono mientras espero a que salga?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:858
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_23c263ad:

    # a "K-Kyou?!"
    a "¡¿K-Kyou?!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:860
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_30eeba60:

    # "Why not thrust its bright screen in front of her startled eyes?"
    "¿Por qué no poner esta brillante pantalla delante de sus atónitos ojos?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:861
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_26dd7881:

    # ks "Look at this, please."
    ks "Mira esto, por favor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:862
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9239ee79:

    # a uniform_down armband_down frown "{cps=15}Kyou, how dare y-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve
    a uniform_down armband_down frown "{cps=15}Kyou, ¿cómo te atre-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:863
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_53b872a3:

    # ks "Shh, watch the spiral, Akiko. See it swirl before your eyes and remember how it catches your attention."
    ks "Shh, mira la espiral, Akiko. Vela girar frente a tus ojos y recuerda cómo atrapa tu atención."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:866
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_06a7111f:

    # ks "Remember how it makes you want to focus on its every detail. How it hypnotizes you so naturally. So easily." with dissolve
    ks "Recuerda cómo te hace querer concentrarte en cada detalle que tiene. Cómo te hipnotiza de forma tan natural. Tan relajante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:865
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_266d4290:

    # a angry "No... n-no, you're tresspassing! Get out!" with dissolve
    a angry "No... ¡n-no, está prohibido que entres aquí! ¡Sal!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:870
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_206e6d0c:

    # ks "So irresistibly. You may try to look away, but the more you try, the more irresistible the spiral becomes." with dissolve
    ks "Tan irresistible. Puedes intentar apartar la mirada, pero entre más lo intentas, más irresistible se vuelve la espiral." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:873
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3eb2de2a:

    # a frown "I'm not... y-you can't just hypnotize me like this, don't be STUPID!" with dissolve
    a frown "No estoy... ¡n-no puedes hipnotizarme así nada más, no seas ESTÚPIDO!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:875
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bfef3506:

    # "Her retort is hardly convincing, and I continue to talk to her in a calm, even, matter-of-fact tone." with dissolve
    "Su réplica no es muy convincente, y yo continúo hablándole en un tono calmado, nivelado y directo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:870
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ae0f7169:

    # "I know exactly what I'm doing."
    "Sé exactamente lo que estoy haciendo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:871
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_83a166ec:

    # ks "You're right, Akiko. I can't just hypnotize you. This will only happen if you let it."
    ks "Tienes razón, Akiko. No puedo hipnotizarte así nada más. Esto solo ocurrirá si tú lo permites."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:872
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_40720654:

    # ks "You know hypnosis can only work on a willing mind. You know you'll never act on a suggestion you don't truly want."
    ks "Sabes que la hipnosis solo funciona en una mente dispuesta. Sabes que nunca actuarás conforme a una sugestión que no quieras en realidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:873
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2ad760a0:

    # ks "But you realize your arms are bound tight to your sides again, don't you? Pressed to your body, just like how I'm holding my phone?"
    ks "Pero te das cuenta de que tus brazos están de nuevo sujetos a tus costados, ¿no es así? ¿Presionados contra tu cuerpo, así como sostengo mi teléfono?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:876
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_29f45fab:

    # "Akiko, staring wide-eyed into the spiral screen, lets out a frightened whimper as she realizes what I'm saying is true." with dissolve
    "Akiko, mirando con asombro en sus ojos la pantalla con la espiral, suelta un aterrado gimoteo al darse cuenta de que lo que digo es cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:877
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ad8e5461:

    # a "No... n-no, that's impossible!"
    a "No... ¡n-no, eso es imposible!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:878
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_78ee2259:

    # ks "You're the one making it possible. Subconsciously you know what you want to do. What you NEED to do."
    ks "Eres tú quien lo vuelve posible. Subconscientemente sabes lo que quieres hacer. Lo que NECESITAS hacer."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:879
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_aa434cca:

    # ks "And there's nothing wrong with accepting what you need, Akiko. It's okay. Everything's going to be okay."
    ks "Y no tiene nada de malo aceptar lo que necesitas, Akiko. Está bien. Todo estará bien."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:899
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_256cf515:

    # a drowsy "K-Kyou please... p-please, don't do this..."
    a drowsy "K-Kyou, por... p-por favor, no hagas esto..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:884
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9b82555a:

    # ks "Everything's fine, Akiko. I'm just showing you my phone. It's up to you how you want to react."
    ks "Todo está bien, Akiko. Yo solo te estoy mostrando mi teléfono. Depende de ti cómo quieras reaccionar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:885
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9a15838b:

    # ks "It's all up to you if you let your arms remain so tightly bound, as if your sensations were still linked to this phone as strongly as they were last night."
    ks "Depende de ti si dejas que tus brazos permanezcan tan firmemente sujetos, como si tus sensaciones siguieran vinculadas a este teléfono con tanta fuerza como anoche."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:886
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cda71b02:

    # ks "It's all up to you if you continue to stare into this inviting, deeply hypnotic spiral you see before your eyes."
    ks "Depende de ti si continúas mirando esta tentadora y profundamente hipnótica espiral que hay frente a tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:887
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_25372ece:

    # ks "And it's all up to you if you want to experience the deeply pleasurable feeling of hypnosis again."
    ks "Y depende de ti si quieres experimentar la profundamente placentera sensación de la hipnosis otra vez."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:888
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c23bc4e0:

    # a "You're... I-I'm not hypnotized... I'm not..."
    a "Estás... N-no estoy hipnotizada... No estoy... "

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:906
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_837b1a26:

    # ks "You're not hypnotized unless you want to be hypnotized." with dissolve
    ks "No estás hipnotizada a no ser que quieras estar hipnotizada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:890
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5126d86e:

    # ks "And you do enjoy the experience of being hypnotized so very much, don't you?"
    ks "Y realmente disfrutas la experiencia de ser hipnotizada, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:913
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c532c390:

    # a "Y-yes... but... but I..." with dissolve
    a "S-sí... pero... pero, eh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:915
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_43e4fa39:

    # "As she stammers, I bring a fingertip to gently rub the top edge of my phone before continuing in my calm, measured voice." with dissolve
    "Mientras tartamudea, froto suavemente con mi dedo la orilla superior de mi teléfono antes de continuar en mi calmada y mesurada voz." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:918
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_48502f65:

    # a blush "A-aahhnnn..."
    a blush "A-aahhnnn..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:898
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c2967a88:

    # ks "You can stop this from happening at any time, Akiko. But it's okay to admit you don't want to."
    ks "Puedes detener esto en cualquier momento, Akiko. Pero está bien admitir que no quieres."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:899
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_60557156:

    # ks "It's okay to admit you want to be drawn into the spiral. It's okay to admit you want to become hypnotized by the spiral once again."
    ks "Está bien admitir que quieres dejarte llevar por la espiral. Está bien admitir que quieres ser hipnotizada par la espiral una vez más."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:904
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7fa45f6d:

    # ks "It's okay to let your desires take over and admit what you really want. Admit what all your senses are telling you."
    ks "Está bien dejar que tus deseos se apoderen de ti y admitir lo que realmente quieres. Admitir lo que tus sentidos te dicen."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:905
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_769e593b:

    # ks "So tell me what it is you really want, Akiko."
    ks "Así que dime qué es lo que realmente quieres, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:906
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a1059f08:

    # a "I want..."
    a "Quiero..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:911
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_165deacd:

    # a "I-I want... to be hypnotized..."
    a "Qu-quiero... ser hipnotizada..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:913
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_32f5880e:

    # "Akiko breathlessly admits the truth as she gazes deeply into the spiral, letting it completely absorb her consciousness." with dissolve
    "Akiko admite jadeante la verdad, observando profundamente la espiral, dejando que absorba por completo su consciencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:914
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_945f9706:

    # ks "Very good, Akiko. Just gaze deep and enjoy the feeling of hypnosis washing over you."
    ks "Muy bien, Akiko. Observa profundamente y disfruta la sensación de hipnosis esparciéndose por todo tu ser."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:915
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_77e5a5d9:

    # "Of course her \"truth\" is a lie I impressed on her. Again, I know what I'm doing."
    "Claro que la \"verdad\" es una mentira impuesta por mí. Una vez más, sé lo que estoy haciendo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:916
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_62be167a:

    # ks "Let yourself drop deeper. Deeper than you've ever been before."
    ks "Déjate caer más profundo. Más profundo que nunca."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:917
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3912db19:

    # "I've seen how the penlight affected her all those days ago. It was the catalyst for all the amazing things she's been capable of under hypnosis ever since."
    "Vi cómo la linterna la afectó hace varios días. Fue el catalizador de todas las maravillas que ha logrado bajo hipnosis desde entonces."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:918
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7c77f842:

    # ks "Letting all your cares and worries disappear into the spiral."
    ks "Deja que todas tus preocupaciones desaparezcan en la espiral."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:952
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0d5d4ed2:

    # "She went from being unable to focus properly at my first attempt at an induction, to going every bit as deep into hypnosis as Hiroko in that alley."
    "Pasó de no poder concentrarse adecuadamente durante mi primer intento de inducción, a caer tan profundo en hipnosis como Hiroko en aquel callejón."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:922
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_eb701a56:

    # ks "Feeling calm, feeling relaxed, feeling completely hypnotized."
    ks "Sintiéndote tranquila, sintiéndote relajada, sintiéndote completamente hipnotizada."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:923
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0a6c748f:

    # "To the point she's compelled to respond to my voodoo phone suggestion as if it were the most irresistibly natural thing in the world."
    "A tal punto que está obligada a responder a mi sugestión del teléfono vudú como si fuera lo más irresistible y natural del mundo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:924
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9244e966:

    # "And finally to the point where I can hypnotize her like a freaking cartoon character."
    "Y finalmente a tan punto que puedo hipnotizarla como un maldito personaje de caricatura."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:925
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_54237e87:

    # ks "Seeing only the spiral. Hearing only my voice."
    ks "Viendo solo la espiral. Escuchando solo mi voz."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:926
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_84b31695:

    # "My penlight made all of it possible. Just like it did with Hiroko."
    "Mi linterna hizo todo esto posible. Justo como hizo con Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:928
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_03c99173:

    # "But now I need to hurry. It won't be long before someone realizes we're missing and comes looking for us."
    "Pero ahora debo apresurarme. No tardarán en darse cuenta de que no estamos y alguien vendrá a buscarnos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:929
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_438328d7:

    # ks "And now that you're so deep in hypnotic trance, so focused on my voice, I need your subconscious to remember something that you need to do after school."
    ks "Y ahora que estás en un profundo trance hipnótico, escuchando solo en mi voz, tu subconsciente debe recordar algo que debes hacer después de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:930
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fae18e43:

    # "I can't do everything I want, but that's okay."
    "No puedo hacer todo lo que quiero, pero no hay problema."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:931
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7889375b:

    # ks "You'll finish your school duties as soon as you can and come see me at my home. You know the way."
    ks "Terminarás con tus deberes de la escuela tan pronto como puedas y vendrás a mi casa. Conoces el camino."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:932
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ab18e0be:

    # "Akiko will make time for me. She has to."
    "Akiko hará tiempo para mí. Tiene que hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:933
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_98e71186:

    # ks "It will never occur to you why you need to do this. You will simply leave school as soon as you can and see me at my home. Understand, Akiko?"
    ks "Nunca pensarás en por qué necesitas hacerlo. Simplemente te irás de las escuela tan pronto como puedas y vendrás a verme a mi casa. ¿Comprendes, Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:934
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1dfc80e8:

    # a entranced_talk "Yes..." with dissolve
    a entranced_talk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:936
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ea568890:

    # ks "Very good, Akiko. You will feel very compelled to act on this suggestion as soon as you can." with dissolve
    ks "Muy bien, Akiko. Sentirás un fuerte impulso de actuar conforme a esta sugestión tan pronto como puedas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:937
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_eaa01a98:

    # ks "Now in a moment I'm going to ask you to count up slowly in your head, from one to twenty."
    ks "En un momento te pediré que cuentes lentamente en tu cabeza del uno al veinte."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:938
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a0f39ae0:

    # ks "As you do, you will find that you have completely forgotten our meeting here today. You will be unable to consciously recall a single thing I have said or done."
    ks "Al hacerlo, olvidarás completamente nuestro encuentro de hoy en este lugar. Serás incapaz de recordar nada de lo que dije o hice."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:939
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b0b10940:

    # ks "And the moment you count the number twenty, you will awaken from this pleasant state of hypnosis feeling good and refreshed."
    ks "Y cuando llegues al número veinte, despertarás de este placentero estado de hipnosis, sintiéndote bien."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:940
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1ed0ffc9:

    # ks "You will continue your day as if nothing strange had occurred. Do you understand?"
    ks "Continuarás tu día como si nada extraño hubiera ocurrido. ¿Comprendes?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:941
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_19114db0:

    # a entranced_talk "Yes... I understand." with dissolve
    a entranced_talk "Sí... Comprendo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:943
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8f74b0d0:

    # ks "That's wonderful, Akiko. Being hypnotized and fully accepting my suggestions really is the best feeling." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso, Akiko. Ser hipnotizada y aceptar plenamente mis sugestiones es la mejor sensación que hay." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:944
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_79cc8843:

    # ks "Now begin counting..."
    ks "Ahora comienza a contar..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:953
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dc4c04c5:

    # "Setting Hiroko free was a mistake. I know that now."
    "Liberar a Hiroko fue un error. Ahora lo sé."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:954
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6446d34f:

    # "I had a chance to change my world and do whatever I wanted, but I let it slip out of some misguided sense of morality."
    "Tuve la oportunidad de cambiar mi mundo y hacer todo lo que me quisiera, pero dejé que se me escapara por un torpe sentido de moral."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:959
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_33390529:

    # "But not this time. Akiko has given me another chance."
    "Pero no esta vez. Akiko me ha dado otra oportunidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:962
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2592ed48:

    # "Whether she realized it or not."
    "Se haya dado cuenta o no."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:967
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_28eb5d7e:

    # "And I won't make that mistake again, Akiko."
    "Y no volveré a cometer ese error, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:968
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_783dcb12:

    # a "Phew. What a day."
    a "Uf. Qué día."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:969
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5fa2e72b:

    # "Not with you."
    "No contigo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:970
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_849eb4dc:

    # a sad_side "Student council was a drag again, but I got here as fast as I could." with dissolve
    a sad_side "El consejo estudiantil otra vez fue un fastidio, pero vine tan rápido como pude." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:971
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fd2a3c86:

    # "I'll never let you go."
    "Nunca te dejaré ir."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:973
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c1612e1b:

    # a sad "Wait... what am I doing here?" with dissolve
    a sad "Espera... ¿qué hago aquí? " with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:974
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3b39e3dc:

    # "I'll make sure of it."
    "Me aseguraré de eso."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:975
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5093bd1a:

    # a surprised "Kyou?" with dissolve
    a surprised "¿Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1015
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bb2741d9:

    # a uniform_down armband_down "{cps=15}Kyou what's going o-{/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    a uniform_down armband_down "{cps=15}Kyou, ¿qué está pa-{/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:979
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4d7ca580:

    # ks neutral "Shh, just stare and sink, Akiko."
    ks neutral "Shh, solo observa y déjate llevar, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:980
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_311f07d7:

    # ks "Everything's fine. All you have to do is relax, stare, and sink back into a pleasant state of hypnotic trance."
    ks "Todo está bien. Solo debes relajarte, observar y dejarte caer de vuelta a un placentero estado de trance hipnótico."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1026
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2ff35139:

    # a entranced_talk "O... okay..."
    a entranced_talk "D-... de acuerdo..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_20536c8c:

    # ks "That's right, Akiko. You can't resist any more. You don't want to resist any more."
    ks "Eso es, Akiko. Ya no puedes resistir. Ya no quieres resistir."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:984
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d7937b3a:

    # ks "So just relax and allow yourself to be pulled deeper into the spiral..."
    ks "Así que relájate y déjate arrastrar más profundo hacia la espiral..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:986
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ef94a9ba:

    # "As she stares lost in my phone's screen for the second time today, I reach over her shoulder and push the front door closed behind her."
    "Mientras observa perdidamente la pantalla de mi teléfono por segunda vez hoy, paso mi mano por encima de su hombro y cierro la puerta detrás de ella."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:988
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9199a0ea:

    # "I may as well have just closed the door to our old lives."
    "Como si estuviera cerrando la puerta a nuestras viejas vidas."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:991
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_91547455:

    # "The next ten minutes pass in a haze of spoken words as I feverishly get to work..."
    "Los siguientes diez minutos pasan en una nube de palabras, pues me pongo fervientemente a trabajar..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:993
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dbfc4a0e:

    # ks "Falling deeper into trance now, Akiko. Ten times deeper. A hundred times deeper."
    ks "Cae más profundo en trance ahora, Akiko. Diez veces más profundo. Cien veces más profundo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:994
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_81f5ae88:

    # ks "And as you fall so very deeply into this pleasant state of trance, I want you to imagine all of your conscious thought start to seep out of you."
    ks "Y al caer tan profundo en este placentero estado de trance, quiero que imagines cómo todos tus pensamientos conscientes comienzan a drenarse."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:995
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9c7b2208:

    # ks "I want you to imagine it leaving your head and draining out into this spiral before you."
    ks "Quiero que los imagines saliendo de tu cabeza y siendo absorbidos por esta espiral que hay frente a ti."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:996
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_786aba74:

    # ks "Can you do that, Akiko?"
    ks "¿Puedes hacer eso, Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:998
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7756caf3:

    # a "Yes..." with dissolve
    a "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1000
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3ff2152e:

    # "I empty her mind completely, leaving it open and able to accept my own ideas. My own designs."
    "Vacío por completo su mente, dejándola abierta para aceptar mis propias ideas. Mi propio diseño."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1020
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6b9185b9:

    # ks "... So do you understand and accept everything you have been told as the truth, Akiko?"
    ks "... Entonces, ¿entiendes y aceptas todo lo que se te dijo como verdad, Akiko?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1021
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2922bbe4:

    # a "Yes. Everything."
    a "Sí. Todo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1022
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f4dac72a:

    # "I'll rewrite her reality."
    "Reescribiré su realidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1023
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1ff216c1:

    # ks "Wonderful. Whether you're deep in hypnotic trance or wide awake and fully alert, you will find you can accept these facts unconditionally."
    ks "Maravilloso. Así estés en un profundo trance hipnótico o despierta y completamente alerta, verás que puedes aceptar estos hechos de forma incondicional."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1028
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ea2ed0f1:

    # ks "No matter how absurd these facts may seem on the surface, no matter how much you may want to deny them, these facts will simply become impossible for you to reject."
    ks "Sin importar lo absurdos que estos hechos puedan parecer en la superficie, sin importar cuánto quieras negarlos, estos hechos simplemente te serán imposibles de rechazar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ebc37d84:

    # "I'll force her to accept it. She'll accept every bit of it."
    "La obligaré a aceptarlo. Aceptará cada pequeño detalle."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1030
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d97fa46d:

    # ks "So now we are going to wake you up slowly as I count up from one. When I reach the number five and snap my fingers, you will awaken..."
    ks "Y ahora despertarás lentamente mientras cuento del uno al cinco. Cuando llegue al número cinco y chasquee mis dedos, estarás despierta..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1042
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d7a287ab:

    # "By the time she goes home tonight, she won't so much as dream of leaving me ever again."
    "Para cuando vaya a casa esta noche, ni siquiera soñará con volverme a dejar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1043
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d7764765:

    # ks "{cps=15}And... {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks "{cps=15}Y... {/cps}{w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1045
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c1c03544:

    # extend "five."
    extend "cinco."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1049
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6718f95d:

    # a "... W-wow, ahahahaha, I really don't know what's going on with me today. This isn't like me at all!"
    a "... G-guau, jajajajaja, en serio no sé qué me pasa hoy. ¡Yo no suelo ser así!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1051
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a4c3ff32:

    # ks smirk "I just can't believe you'd walk all this way to see me and completely forget your purpose. Are you normally this scatterbrained?"
    ks smirk "No puedo creer que caminaras hasta acá para verme y olvidaras completamente tu propósito. ¿Sueles ser tan despistada?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1053
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9d400941:

    # "Akiko shakes her head bashfully as I playfully admonish her." with dissolve
    "Akiko sacude la cabeza apenada al oír mi burlona amonestación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1054
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_daa02306:

    # a "I'm not making a good impression, am I? As if forgetting the rules wasn't bad enough."
    a "No estoy dando una buena impresión, ¿verdad? Y para colmo olvidé las reglas."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1056
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_610239cb:

    # a "\"No school attire and no glasses\"." with dissolve
    a "\"No se puede entrar con uniforme escolar ni anteojos.\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1058
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_95269764:

    # a "I'm really near-sighted, but... I could put my contacts in? I have a pair in my bag, I promise I'll be quick." with dissolve
    a "Estoy bastante miope, pero... ¿Tal vez pueda ponerme mis contactos? Tengo un par en mi mochila, prometo que será rápido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1059
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_de9e96bf:

    # ks smile "That won't be necessary."
    ks smile "Eso no será necesario."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1060
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e4832c45:

    # a "{cps=20}Okay... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    a "{cps=20}Bueno... {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1063
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b72a316c:

    # extend "Oh! And I'm supposed to be meeting my parents for dinner in an hour so I can't stay out too late. Does that leave me enough time for this?"
    extend "¡Oh! Y debo llegar con mis padres para cenar en una hora, así que no puedo quedarme hasta muy tarde. ¿Eso me deja tiempo suficiente para esto?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1064
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_52e44e11:

    # ks "Ah... yeah, this won't take too long. Don't worry."
    ks "Ah... seh, esto no tardará mucho. Descuida."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1066
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5d1f118f:

    # a "Be honest with me... have I blown it already?" with dissolve
    a "Sé honesto conmigo... ¿ya lo eché a perder?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1068
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_66e99c5f:

    # a "I-I really can't apologize enough. I'm usually way more put together than this..." with dissolve
    a "E-en serio, mil disculpas. Suelo ser más responsable que esto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1070
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f7ca8cd2:

    # a "I've just been having a really hard time of it lately, that's all." with dissolve
    a "Es que he estado pasando por cosas difíciles últimamente, es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1084
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fa1704dd:

    # a "O-of course I didn't mean to say that's an excuse or anything! It's just... u-uhh..." with dissolve
    a "¡C-claro, no digo que sea excusa ni nada! Es que... e-eeh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1085
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dd48236d:

    # "I raise my hand to quiet her as a kind smile spreads across my lips. Although I'm not convinced she can see my expression with that dim eyesight of hers."
    "Alzo una mano para silenciarla con una amable sonrisa dibujándose en mis labios. Aunque no sé si pueda ver mi expresión con su vista borrosa."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1086
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ad7b3e78:

    # ks "Okay, I'm going to stop you right there. Just take a few moments to breathe and relax. You haven't screwed this up."
    ks "Bien, voy a detenerte ahí. Solo tómate un momento para respirar y relajarte. Aún no has arruinado esto."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1088
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8430b1d4:

    # ks "As far as I'm concerned you're here now and we'll overlook that you came here in a school uniform of all things. What you're wearing now is a good compromise." with dissolve
    ks "En cuanto a mí concierne, estás aquí ahora y pasaremos por alto que te apareciste con ese uniforme escolar. Lo que llevas puesto ahora es un buen compromiso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1089
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_72d36c77:

    # ks "So as soon as you're ready we can get started and we'll be done before dinner. Okay?"
    ks "Así que, si estás lista para comenzar, terminaremos a tiempo para la cena. ¿De acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1091
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_86dc8cdb:

    # "I can see her chest rise as she takes a deep breath through her nose, managing to settle at least some of those nerves of hers." with dissolve
    "Puedo ver su pecho elevarse al respirar hondo por su nariz, logrando calmar esos nervios al menos un poco." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1093
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8caa8326:

    # a "Okay, thank you... I'm ready."
    a "De acuerdo, gracias... Estoy lista."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1094
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_112e80ba:

    # ks "Very good. Start by telling me your full name and your purpose for being here tonight."
    ks "Muy bien. Primero dime tu nombre completo y tu razón de estar aquí esta noche."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1096
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d01018d7:

    # a "... My name is Akiko Tsushima, and I'm here to apply for the position of \"Kyou's Girlfriend\"." with dissolve
    a "Mi nombre es Akiko Tsushima, y estoy aquí para aplicar para el puesto de \"Novia de Kyou\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1097
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_607f14fd:

    # "I can't help it, I'm grinning like a maniac hearing those words. And I'm feeling a lot better about taking her glasses now so she can't see it."
    "No puedo evitarlo, estoy sonriendo como maniaco al oír esas palabras. Me alegra mucho haberle quitado los anteojos, así no podrá verlo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1098
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0fb88639:

    # "Akiko's clearly out of her depth and embarrassed as hell, but most importantly it's clear she's completely accepting the reality I've created for her."
    "Akiko está claramente fuera de su elemento y muy avergonzada, pero lo más importante, está claro que acepta la realidad que creé para ella."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1100
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_37fec480:

    # ks "And what qualifications can you bring to the table, Tsushima?"
    ks "¿Y qué capacitaciones tienes para ofrecer, Tsushima?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1103
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_27e5b476:

    # a "Well, firstly I'm eighteen years old and a high-school senior, just like Kyou... um, you." with dissolve
    a "Bueno, para empezar tengo dieciocho años de edad y estoy en último año de preparatoria igual que Kyou... em, tú." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1105
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_deef4efa:

    # a "I'm the president of our school's student council, and I'm a member of a weekend kendo club, so I live a very active and healthy lifestyle." with dissolve
    a "Soy la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, y soy miembro de un club de kendo de fines de semana, por lo que llevo un estilo de vida muy activo y saludable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1107
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f73f404c:

    # a "Plus I have a wide range of interests besides that, including hypnosis, literature and videogames. And I'm always eager to learn new things." with dissolve
    a "Y tengo un amplio rango de intereses además de esos, incluyendo hipnosis, literatura y videojuegos. Y siempre me entusiasma aprender cosas nuevas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1173
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2f633ec1:

    # ks smirk "But most importantly are you interested in guys? Sexually, I mean?"
    ks smirk "Pero más importante, ¿te interesan los varones? Ya sabes, ¿sexualmente?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1175
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a46113fc:

    # a "A-ahahahaha, of course! I-I-I LOVE guys~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a "¡A-ajajajaja, por supuesto! ¡A-A-ADORO a los varones! {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1111
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5e990e9d:

    # ks "And if I offered you the position, you'd be able to start right away?"
    ks "¿Y si te ofreciera el puesto, podrías comenzar de inmediato?"
# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1113
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_370f4830:

    # a "Yes, absolutely. I'm currently single, so that won't be an issue for me." with dissolve
    a "Sí, absolutamente. Actualmente estoy soltera, así que eso no será un problema para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1114
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_37036583:

    # "Nodding and stroking my chin sagely, I suck in a sharp breath as I try to endure the excitement building up in my crotch."
    "Asintiendo y frotando sagazmente mi barbilla, tomo aire agudamente intentando, contener la emoción que crece en mi entrepierna."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1115
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6216f664:

    # "Really wish I'd known how long we had together before I thought to enact this mental exercise on her."
    "Ojalá hubiera sabido cuánto tiempo teníamos antes de llevar a cabo este ejercicio mental con ella."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1116
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ee3fa2ce:

    # "Well... there'll be time to satisfy my urges soon. Tomorrow, even."
    "Bueno... pronto habrá tiempo de satisfacer mis impulsos. Tal vez mañana."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1117
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_958f6841:

    # ks frown "I... h-have a few questions about your application, Tsushima."
    ks frown "Tengo... u-unas cuantas preguntas sobre tu solicitud, Tsushima."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1118
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_89b98e93:

    # "For now, I'll just have to focus on affirming Akiko's new identity, like I planned."
    "Por ahora, tendré que enfocarme en afirmar la nueva identidad de Akiko, como lo planeé."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1120
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d6e3ae03:

    # a "Oh, sure! Ask me anything!" with dissolve
    a "¡Oh, claro! ¡Pregúntame lo que sea!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1121
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_15f38c91:

    # ks "So you said you lead an active lifestyle and you're a member of two extra-curricular clubs."
    ks "Dijiste que llevabas un estilo de vida activo y que eres miembro de dos clubes extracurriculares."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1123
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_84970133:

    # a "Mhm, that's right~" with dissolve
    a "Mjm, es correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1124
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_28fb861f:

    # ks "It just concerns me that you haven't necessarily thought about the level of commitment I'll need from someone taking this position."
    ks "Es que me preocupa que tal vez no hayas pensado en el nivel de compromiso que necesito de alguien en esta posición."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1126
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_995c0244:

    # a "Oh... r-really?" with dissolve
    a "Oh... ¿e-en serio?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1127
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b2a67fd3:

    # ks "Look, if someone's going to be my girlfriend I expect nothing but their absolute loyalty and devotion. They have to give me 100%% at all times."
    ks "Mira, si alguien va a ser mi novia, espero su absoluta lealtad y devoción. Debe darme su 100%% en todo momento."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1128
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f21c7607:

    # ks "So let's say I told you to quit both your clubs. Give up your \"active and healthy lifestyle\" so we can hang out some more. How would you respond to that?"
    ks "Así que, digamos que te digo que renuncies a ambos clubes. Que abandones tu \"estilo de vida saludable\" para que podamos pasar más tiempo juntos."
    ks "¿Cómo responderías a eso?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1130
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_39f77002:

    # a "I... I-I'd quit, of course!" with dissolve
    a "Eh... ¡R-renunciaría, por supuesto!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1131
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_68ac1824:

    # ks "You'd quit?"
    ks "¿Renunciarías?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1132
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_20999bbc:

    # a "I'll turn in my resignations first thing tomorrow morning! I'll even tell them I'm quitting to spend time with my new boyfriend. It's no problem at all, I swear!"
    a "¡Presentaría mi renuncia mañana en la mañana! Incluso les diría que es para pasar más tiempo con mi nuevo novio. ¡No es ningún problema, lo juro!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1133
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9a802230:

    # "I smile at her, satisfied."
    "Le sonrío, satisfecho."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:890
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e4befdbe:

    # "Not that I'm planning to have her do that; too much unwanted attention. But it's encouraging that she'll abandon her attachments without a thought if I tell her."
    "No es que planee que haga eso; demasiada atención no deseada, pero es alentador que abandonaría sus ataduras sin pensarlo dos veces si se lo ordenara."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1135
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_69392d54:

    # ks smile "I'll take that under consideration. So moving on, I want to talk about what interests you."
    ks smile "Tomaré eso en consideración. Prosigamos. Quiero hablar de tus intereses."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1136
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dbf2a58a:

    # ks "You mentioned hypnosis, right?"
    ks "Mencionaste hipnosis, ¿verdad?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1138
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_194ea8a5:

    # a "A-ah, yes, that's right." with dissolve
    a "A-ah, sí, es correcto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1139
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ab43a0c6:

    # ks "Tell me more about that."
    ks "Háblame más de eso."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1141
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_124a80b4:

    # a "Okay... So, hypnosis is about entering an enhanced state of focus. To an outside observer it often looks like someone under hypnosis is asleep." with dissolve
    a "Muy bien... Pues, la hipnosis se trata de entrar a un estado de concentración aumentada. Para un espectador suele parecer que alguien bajo hipnosis está dormido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1143
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_01640485:

    # a "But in fact, a subject under hypnosis is hyper aware and extremely suggestible." with dissolve
    a "Pero, de hecho, un sujeto bajo hipnosis está hiper-consciente y es extremadamente sugestionable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1145
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e54df37d:

    # a "A good hypnotist can effect changes in a subject's behaviour that might have been impossible outside of hypnosis." with dissolve
    a "Un buen hipnotista puede efectuar cambios en el comportamiento de un sujeto que podrían haber sido imposible fuera de la hipnosis." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1146
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_34317996:

    # ks smirk "So... mind control?"
    ks smirk "O sea... ¿control mental?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1148
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_af58c58d:

    # "Akiko giggles gently." with dissolve
    "Akiko se ríe suavemente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1150
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bbaec589:

    # a "N-no, hahaha~ You can't use hypnosis to control people like you see in the movies. It's a common misconception." with dissolve
    a "N-no, jajaja. No puedes usar hipnosis para controlar a la gente como en las películas. Eso es un mito muy común." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1152
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a8b01284:

    # a "Anything a person subject to hypnosis agrees to and acts upon is completely down to them. A hypnotist can't force them to do anything they don't want to." with dissolve
    a "Todo lo que una persona sujeta a hipnosis acepte o haga depende enteramente de ella. Un hipnotista no puede forzarla a hacer nada que no quiera." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1153
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_67be61d5:

    # ks smile "I see. That sounds fascinating, but how did you pick up an interest like that?"
    ks smile "Ya veo. Eso suena fascinante, ¿pero que causó ese interés en ti?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1155
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_044cc8ec:

    # a "Ah well, I'm a student of psychology, you see. I've always been interested in subjects of the mind. But hypnosis specifically is... um, a recent thing for me." with dissolve
    a "Oh, bueno, soy estudiante de psicología. Siempre me ha interesado el tema de la mente. Pero la hipnosis específicamente es... em, algo reciente para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1157
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c2c60363:

    # a "I actually didn't know much about hypnosis until a week ago when a certain someone introduced me to it, and... w-well..." with dissolve
    a "De hecho no sabía mucho de hipnosis hasta hace una semana cuando cierta persona me introdujo al tema, y... b-bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1159
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_92b928b9:

    # a "It's something I'm really passionate about now!" with dissolve
    a "¡Es algo que ahora me apasiona mucho!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1162
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d9d545aa:

    # ks "Passionate, huh? Are you studying to be a hypnotist, then?"
    ks "Te apasiona, ¿eh? ¿Entones estudiarás para ser hipnotista?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1164
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_88a921f1:

    # "I pause to allow Akiko to cheerfully correct me." with dissolve
    "Hago una pausa para dejar que Akiko me corrija alegremente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1166
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f6067dcd:

    # a "No, sir. I'm passionate about BEING hypnotized!" with dissolve
    a "No, Señor. ¡Me apasiona SER hipnotizada!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1169
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_014eae86:

    # ks smirk "Now you're speaking my language. Any girlfriend of mine needs to be extremely hypnotizeable."
    ks smirk "Ahora sí hablas mi idioma. Cualquier novia mia debe ser extremadamente hipnotizable."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1170
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0db8e1b3:

    # ks "Because... yeah, let's stop being coy around each other here."
    ks "Porque... seh, ya dejemos de cohibirnos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1171
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7da66df4:

    # ks "You know I was only testing you just now. After all, I'm the one who introduced you to the subject. I'm your hypnotist."
    ks "Sabes que solo te estaba probando. Después de todo, yo soy quien te introdujo al tema. Yo soy tu hipnotista."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1173
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bda36798:

    # a "Ehehe, yup~" with dissolve
    a "Jejeje, sipi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1174
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0bbf4857:

    # ks "So let me ask you, Tsushima: How hypnotizeable do you think you are?"
    ks "Así que déjame preguntarte, Tsushima: ¿Qué tan hipnotizable eres?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1176
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_21e437dc:

    # a "Oh... that's a good question." with dissolve
    a "Oh... buena pregunta." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1177
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f93ba2e5:

    # ks smile "And I want you to know there's no right or wrong answer here. Be honest."
    ks smile "Y quiero que sepas que no hay respuesta correcta ni incorrecta. Sé honesta."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1178
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1a2310fc:

    # a "Well I mean, I know for a fact I can be hypnotized."
    a "Pues, bueno, sé que sí puedo ser hipontizada."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1180
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_24c06685:

    # a "And I think I'm responding pretty well to post-hypnotic suggestion, plus you even successfully performed hypnotherapy on me yesterday." with dissolve
    a "Y creo que estoy respondiendo muy bien a sugestiones posthipnóticas, sin mencionar que hasta aplicaste hipnoterapia exitosamente en mí ayer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1182
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d06e0b99:

    # a "S-so if I had to guess..." with dissolve
    a "A-así que si tuviera que adivinar..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1184
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_39db2368:

    # a "I want to say above average?" with dissolve
    a "¿Diría que por encima del promedio?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1185
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_32d09817:

    # "Wonderful. She really has no conscious idea of how much I've gotten in her head."
    "Maravilloso. No tiene idea consciente de lo mucho que me he metido en su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1186
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_421d90b6:

    # ks smile "I'd agree with that assessment. And your hypnotizability is something we can work on."
    ks smile "Puedo concordar con esa declaración. Y tu hipnotizabilidad es algo en lo que podemos trabajar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1187
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6e1a58e6:

    # ks "We'll make hypnosis part of your daily routine. Take you deeper into trance, do a lot of fractionation, really immerse you in it."
    ks "Haremos de la hipnosis parte de nuestra rutina diaria. Ponerte más profundo en trance, fraccionarte, realmente sumergirte en ello."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1188
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d15442a0:

    # ks "I'm sure we can get you from \"above average\" to \"extremely\" in no time. How does that sound?"
    ks "Estoy seguro de que podemos llevarte de \"por encima del promedio\" a \"extremadamente\" en un santiamén. ¿Cómo suena eso?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1190
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3240593b:

    # a "Ahh, that sounds amazing~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a "Aah, suena estupendo. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1191
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b7ac8b73:

    # ks smirk "Heh. I have to say it's encouraging to hear you enjoy being hypnotized. I know a lot of your peers don't feel the same way."
    ks smirk "Je. He de decir que es alentador oír que disfrutas ser hipnotizada. Sé que muchas de tus compañeras no se sienten igual."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1192
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8bb50634:

    # "Bringing up my past misdeeds. Another test for her newfound sense of reality."
    "Saco a tema mis pasadas fechorías. Otra prueba de su nuevo sentido de la realidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1194
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a86053e0:

    # a "Yes, well... hypnosis isn't for everyone." with dissolve
    a "Sí, pues... la hipnosis no es para todos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1195
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0f28e666:

    # ks neutral "Right. So I know you're aware I approached other... candidates for this position before opening it up to applicants such as yourself."
    ks neutral "Cierto. Y sé que estás enterada de que me aproximé a otras... candidatas para esta posición antes de abrirla a aplicantes como tú."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1206
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7ecb0843:

    # a "... Hiroko Homura and Nozomi Akemi." with dissolve
    a "... Hiroko Homura y Nozomi Akemi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1207
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b25937c5:

    # ks "That's right. I tried to hypnotize Nozomi into becoming my girlfriend and Hiroko into..."
    ks "Correcto. Intenté hipnotizar a Nozomi para ser mi novia y Hiroko para ser..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1209
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_718d5cb7:

    # a "Your slave? That's what she said, wasn't it?" with dissolve
    a "¿Tu esclava? Eso es lo que dijo, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1210
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_86b0e29b:

    # ks sigh "... Yeah, let's go with that."
    ks sigh "... Sí, pongámoslo así."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1211
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e9625d42:

    # "Gotta admit, I'm very interested to find out how her mind will reconcile the facts of our past with the lies I fed her mind."
    "Debo admitir que estoy muy interesado en averiguar cómo reconciliará su mente los hechos del pasado con las mentiras que planté en su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1212
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_22367048:

    # "But I know she won't disappoint me."
    "Pero sé que no me decepcionará."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1213
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_90f97f70:

    # ks neutral "Last time we talked it sure seemed you wanted nothing more to do with me. But now you're interviewing to be my girlfriend?"
    ks neutral "La última vez que lo discutimos vaya que parecía que no querías estar cerca de mí nunca más. ¿Pero ahora estás en una entrevista para ser mi novia?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1214
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a3c71864:

    # ks "Can you explain your thought process behind that?"
    ks "¿Puedes explicar tu línea de pensamiento?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1216
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e515625e:

    # a "Y-yes... I really was so angry with you. I won't deny it." with dissolve
    a "S-sí... estaba muy enojada contigo. No lo negaré." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1217
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a2952b3d:

    # a "But after I had time to reflect on that stressful situation with Hiroko, I realized I let my emotions get the better of me."
    a "Pero una vez tuve tiempo de reflexionar sobre esa estresante situación con Hiroko, me di cuenta de que dejé que mis emociones sacaran lo peor de mí."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1219
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4773c82b:

    # a "You were a real jerk to her, trying to hypnotize her without her consent like that. But the fact is what she said happened to her is impossible." with dissolve
    a "Fuiste un gran cretino con ella, intentando hipnotizarla así sin su consentimiento. Pero el hecho es que lo que dijo que le ocurrió es imposible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1221
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_10e69956:

    # a "She was just scared of your light because she believed those stupid misconceptions I was talking about!" with dissolve
    a "¡Simplemente la asustaba tu luz porque creía esos estúpidos mitos de los que hablaba!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1223
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f7c00a5d:

    # a "And the more I thought about it, the more I didn't think it was fair to hold you fully responsible for her extreme reaction to what you did." with dissolve
    a "Y entre más lo pensaba, menos me parecía justo responsabilizarte por su extrema reacción hacia lo que hiciste." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1224
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_03863a6c:

    # ks sigh "It's a shame you didn't have this epiphany BEFORE you reported me to the principal."
    ks sigh "Es una pena que no tuvieras esta epifanía ANTES de reportarme con el director."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1225
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b2366159:

    # ks "And I can't just overlook the role you played in getting me suspended from our school."
    ks "Y no puedo pasar por alto el papel que jugaste en hacer que me suspendieran de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1226
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1f9dc683:

    # "I look her over sternly, and she trembles in turn. It's the moment of truth, Tsushima."
    "La miro con severidad, y ella tiembla en respuesta. Es el momento de la verdad, Tsushima."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1227
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8384c72e:

    # ks frown "You understand this puts your application at a serious disadvantage. So tell me, why should I choose you above anyone else?"
    ks frown "Entiendes que esto pone tu aplicación en seria desventaja. Así que, dime, ¿por qué debería escogerte por sobre a alguien más?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1228
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cf0911b9:

    # "Show me how well you've accepted my lies."
    "Muéstrame lo bien que as aceptado mis mentiras."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1230
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_557a047f:

    # a "... I really am so sorry, Kyou. I know I was weak when you needed me to be strong." with dissolve
    a "... Realmente lo siento, Kyou. Sé que fui débil cuando me necesitabas fuerte." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1232
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_83f2e1ce:

    # a "So I promise, I'll never doubt you ever again. I'll always take your side, no matter what." with dissolve
    a "Así que prometo que nunca volveré a dudar de ti. Siempre estaré de tu lado, no importa qué." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1339
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1414456a:

    # a "I'll always protect you from now on!" with dissolve
    a "¡Siempre te protegeré de ahora en adelante!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1235
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2ca11450:

    # "Just then, Akiko leans forward, her hands pawing at my shoulders as she looks to me with need in her unfocused eyes."
    "En ese momento, Akiko se inclina hacia adelante, poniendo sus manos sobre mis hombros, mirándome con necesidad en sus desenfocados ojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1237
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_779769c1:

    # a "I... I love you, Kyou Koyama. Please make me your girlfriend." with dissolve
    a "Te... te amo, Kyou Koyama. Por favor acéptame como tu novia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1238
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1592d665:

    # "She stumbles forward, her forehead almost knocking against mine while she clumsily plants a knee on the coffee table between us."
    "Da un traspié hacia adelante, su cabeza casi choca con la mía mientras coloca torpemente una rodilla en la mesa de centro que hay entre nosotros."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1352
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_81c87a5e:

    # a "I'll give you one-hundred percent commitment, just like you want. Everything I have, it's yours." with dissolve
    a "Y te daré cien por ciento de compromiso, justo como quieres. Todo lo que tengo, es tuyo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1240
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ab32928c:

    # "Her lips linger near mine. I can feel her breath as she makes her pleas..."
    "Sus labios permanecen cerca de los míos. Puedo sentir su aliento mientras hace sus súplicas..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1241
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a6272673:

    # a "I'll cherish every waking moment we can be together. I'll dream of you every moment we're apart."
    a "Apreciaré cada momento consciente que podamos pasar juntos. Soñaré contigo cada momento que estemos lejos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1243
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4dcec33f:

    # a "Hypnotize me. Make me your slave if that will make you happy. Anything you want."
    a "Hipnotízame. Hazme tu esclava si eso te hará feliz. Lo que sea que tú quieras."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1364
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7d799bae:

    # "... and before my brain registers the sensation, I feel her lips too."
    "... y antes de que mi cerebro pueda procesar la sensación, también siento sus labios."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1246
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_896cb137:

    # "She kisses me deeply, and I have no intention of stopping her from showing me her need. Her newfound hunger. Her desperation to please..."
    "Me besa profundamente, y no tengo intención de evitar que me muestre su necesidad. Su nuevo apetito. Su desesperación por complacer..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1247
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_78961072:

    # "... I guess I'll offer her the job on a trial basis. See how it goes."
    "... Supongo que le ofreceré el empleo en fase de prueba. A ver qué tal va."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1248
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dd1e91bb:

    # a "Just let me be with you. I need you..."
    a "Solo déjame estar contigo. Te necesito..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1251
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_aeeb224b:

    # a "I love you..."
    a "Te amo..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1252
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d9bc9eb4:

    # "AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's all the script I have for now!"
    "NOTA DE LA AUTORA: ¡Y ese es todo el texto que tengo por ahora!"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1253
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_51423782:

    # "Read on to read the outline for the epilogue of this story path, which will be finished for the next update."
    "A continuación el bosquejo del epílogo de esta historia, el cual estará listo para la próxima actualización."

