# game/Kyou 9.rpy:883
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fb430b1b:

    # "She's been struggling to reach out with her right hand, whether to cover her eyes or make a grab for my phone, all while unconsciously restraining herself."
    "Ha estado intentando alzar su mano derecha, ya sea para cubrirse los ojos o tomar mi teléfono, pero se restringe subconscientemente."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:884
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6cca99cf:

    # "But now she's beginning to understand."
    "Pero ahora empieza a comprender."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:892
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_860aa0bb:

    # a "No, it's not... th-this isn't happening... this isn't..."
    a "No, no es-... e-esto no está pasando... esto no..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:900
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5219a9ec:

    # ks "You're the only one who can do it, Akiko. It's all up to you if you continue to stare into this inviting, deeply hypnotic spiral you see before your eyes."
    ks "Tú eres la única que puede hacerlo, Akiko. Depende de ti si continúas mirando esta tentadora y profundamente hipnótica espiral que hay frente a tus ojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:904
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8ccf169b:

    # a "You're... I-I'm not hypnotized... I'm not... h-hypnotized, I'm not..."
    a "Estás... N-no estoy hipnotizada... No estoy... hi-hipnotizada, no estoy..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:920
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_77b1a7b9:

    # a "I don't... aahhh, d-don't..."
    a "N-no... aaaah, n-no..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:939
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c27bba46:

    # ks "It feels wonderful to admit what you want, doesn't it?"
    ks "Se siente maravilloso admitir lo que quieres, ¿no es así?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:941
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_91114a02:

    # a "Yes... wonderful..." with dissolve
    a "Sí... maravilloso..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:943
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_188a9140:

    # ks "You want to be hypnotized by the spiral." with dissolve
    ks "Quieres ser hipnotizada por la espiral." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:945
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_810b46e0:

    # a "I want to be hypnotized by the spiral..." with dissolve
    a "Quiero ser hipnotizada por la espiral..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:947
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4dff7ae5:

    # ks "Feeling wonderful as you let yourself drop deeper, Akiko. Deeper than you've ever been before." with dissolve
    ks "Se siente maravilloso dejarte caer más profundo, Akiko. Más profundo de lo que jamás has estado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:978
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5a13d97b:

    # ks "That's wonderful, Akiko. Being hypnotized and fully accepting my suggestions really is the best feeling in the world." with dissolve
    ks "Maravilloso, Akiko. Ser hipnotizada y aceptar plenamente mis sugestiones es la mejor sensación del mundo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1018
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_795df317:

    # a angry "{cps=15}What? No! I- {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve
    a angry "{cps=15}¿Qué? ¡No! Ah- {/cps}{w=1.0}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1019
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8e7b1fba:

    # ks "Just relax and sink. You don't want to fight it."
    ks "Solo relájate y déjate llevar. Tú no quieres luchar."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1022
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b875f760:

    # a drowsy "{cps=15}But I... w-wow, that's... {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}"
    a drowsy "{cps=15}Pero si... g-guau, esto... {/cps}{w=1.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1023
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0b2c14c9:

    # ks "Relax and sink. Let the spiral take you deep. Okay?"
    ks "Relájate y déjate llevar. Deja que la espiral te lleve muy profundo. ¿De acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1102
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_74159ff5:

    # a "\"No school attire and no glasses\". That's what they said..." with dissolve
    a "\"No se puede entrar con uniforme escolar ni anteojos\". Eso fue lo que dijeron..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1116
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b0ab52fd:

    # a "I've just been having a really hard time of it lately, as you probably know." with dissolve
    a "Es que he pasado por cosas muy complicadas últimamente, como bien sabrás." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1134
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9be3a66e:

    # ks "As far as I'm concerned you're here now and we'll overlook that you came here in a school uniform of all things." with dissolve
    ks "En cuanto a mí concierne, estás aquí ahora y pasaremos por alto que te apareciste con ese uniforme escolar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1135
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_53611901:

    # ks "Besides, I'm really impressed with how quickly you thought to take it all off as a compromise."
    ks "Además, estoy realmente impresionado por lo rápido que decidiste quitártelo todo como compromiso."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1166
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1ee41fa3:

    # a "I'm also the president of our school's student council, and I'm a member of a weekend kendo club." with dissolve
    a "También soy presidenta del consejo estudiantil de nuestra escuela, y miembro de un club de kendo los fines de semana." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1168
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_857b31bd:

    # a "Both contribute to an active and healthy lifestyle that I believe makes me well-suited to meet any of your physical, mental or spiritual needs." with dissolve
    a "Ambos contribuyen a un estilo de vida activo y saludable que, considero, me adecúa para satisfacer todas tus necesidades físicas, mentales y espirituales." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1191
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c984722e:

    # ks "Not to mention the fact you're still in high school and I'm... w-well, not."
    ks "Sin mencionar el hecho de que sigues en la preparatoria y yo... p-pues, no."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1203
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_93772e8c:

    # ks "Well, I'm sure you know that any girlfriend of mine has to be extremely willing to be hypnotized, so it'll be good if you can hit the ground running."
    ks "Bueno, has de saber que cualquier novia mía debe estar extremadamente dispuesta a ser hipnotizada, por lo que sería bueno que pudieras comenzar con buen pie."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1204
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_bb656dc7:

    # ks "I'd like you to tell me what you know of hypnosis, in your own words."
    ks "Quiero que me digas lo que sepas sobre hipnosis, en tus propias palabras."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1218
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e12e45e6:

    # ks smile "I see. Well you're right, Tsushima, but how does a high school girl like you become interested in hypnosis?"
    ks smile "Ya veo. Bueno, tienes razón, Tsushima, pero ¿qué hizo que una estudiante como tú adquiriera interés por la hipnosis?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1222
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_869bd4a5:

    # a "I actually didn't know much about hypnosis until a week ago when a certain classmate of mine introduced me to it, and... w-well..." with dissolve
    a "De hecho no sabía mucho de hipnosis hasta hace una semana cuando cierto compañero de clase me introdujo al tema, y... b-bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1239
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d1a0a929:

    # ks smirk "Now you're speaking my language. Any girlfriend of mine needs to be not only willing to be hypnotized, but also extremely hypnotizeable."
    ks smirk "Ahora sí hablas mi idioma. Cualquier novia mía no solo debe estar dispuesta a ser hipnotizada, sino también ser extremadamente hipnotizable."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1244
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_30de3f44:

    # ks smile "So in that case let me ask you, Tsushima: How hypnotizeable do you think you are?"
    ks smile "Por lo tanto, permíteme preguntarte, Tsushima: ¿Qué tan hipnotizable crees que eres?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1250
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_747098cf:

    # a "And I think I respond pretty well to post-hypnotic suggestion, plus you even successfully performed hypnotherapy on me yesterday." with dissolve
    a " Y creo que respondo muy bien a sugestiones posthipnóticas, sin mencionar que hasta aplicaste hipnoterapia exitosamente en mí ayer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1319
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c30fe3de:

    # a "Y-yes... I really was so angry with you." with dissolve
    a "S-sí... Estaba muy enojada contigo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1321
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7e2077d6:

    # a "Becoming your girlfriend felt like the furthest thing from my mind. I won't deny it." with dissolve
    a "Volverme tu novia era lo último que se me habría ocurrido. No lo negaré." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1310
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_afcdd3eb:

    # a "I... I love you, Kyou Koyama. I mean it with all my heart, so please... m-make me your girlfriend."
    a "T-... te amo, Kyou Koyama. Lo digo de todo corazón, así que por favor... ha-hazme tu novia."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1349
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7d85e292:

    # a "Hypnotize me all day and night. Make me your slave if that will make you happy."
    a "Hipnotízame día y noche. Vuélveme tu esclava si eso te hará feliz."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1350
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c1b0a667:

    # a "I'll do anything you want."
    a "Haré lo que sea que tú quieras."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1363
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7fc79dff:

    # a "... There. My task has been completed."
    a "... Listo. Mi tarea ha sido completada."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1365
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_da2cd825:

    # ks smile "I can see that. Wasn't hard at all, was it?"
    ks smile "Ya veo que sí. No fue tan difícil, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1367
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7f58efba:

    # "Akiko shakes her head gently as I address her." with dissolve
    "Akiko sacude suavemente la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1368
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b4e209bb:

    # a "You're right, it wasn't."
    a "Tienes razón, no lo fue."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1369
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_858f9130:

    # ks "You really expected it to be difficult?"
    ks "¿Esperabas que fuera complicado?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1371
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a049eacb:

    # a "Yup, I did. I mean, I'm the student council president, and a girl and you're..." with dissolve
    a "Sipi. Pues, soy la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, y una chica y tú eres..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1373
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f6587353:

    # a "Well, you're a guy I've only known a few days telling me to take my clothes off." with dissolve
    a "Bueno, eres un chico que apenas he conocido un par de días diciéndome que me quite la ropa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1374
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4a39845c:

    # ks "And your glasses."
    ks "Y los anteojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1376
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9bf4fcd1:

    # a "And my glasses." with dissolve
    a "Y los anteojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1377
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_66e985e6:

    # "I look aside to her discarded school uniform, folded neatly on the floor and embellished with her student council armband and folded-up pair of specs."
    "Echo un vistazo a su descartado uniforme escolar, pulcramente doblado en el suelo y decorado con su banda del consejo estudiantil y sus gafas plegadas."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1379
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b3315ce1:

    # a "Speaking of, I don't understand why I need those things. Shouldn't someone like me have 20-20 vision?" with dissolve
    a "Hablando de eso, no entiendo por qué necesito esas cosas. ¿No debería alguien como yo tener visión 20-20?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1380
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f3b93c28:

    # ks smile "Ah, not exactly. There had to be a few defects designed for the sake of your disguise."
    ks smile "Ah, no exactamente. Hubo que diseñar algunos defectos para mantener la farsa."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1382
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ba9fd43a:

    # a "Oh... yes, I suppose that does make sense." with dissolve
    a "Oh... sí, supongo que tiene sentido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1383
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0e3e4ffb:

    # ks "You're ordinary, even if you're really not."
    ks "Eres ordinaria, y a la vez no."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1387
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4dd018c8:

    # a "I'm... not like the other girls, that's for sure." with dissolve
    a "No soy... como las otras chicas, eso es seguro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1392
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fd1831f4:

    # ks smile "So remind me again, Akiko: What are you?"
    ks smile "Entonces, recuérdame otra vez, Akiko: ¿Qué eres?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1394
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9104b66a:

    # "She looks to me gently as she quietly admits her truth." with dissolve
    "Me mira gentilmente, admitiendo sin demora la verdad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1395
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_140ffec5:

    # a "I am a [hypno6]. I was built with the latest technology to replicate the human female form."
    a "Soy un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. Fui fabricada con lo último en tecnología para replicar la forma humana femenina."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1396
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c7b3510d:

    # "I beam at her with pride. So far she's accepted every bit of her reprogramming without a hitch."
    "Le sonrío con orgullo. Hasta ahora ha aceptado cada detalle de su programación sin problemas."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1397
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f5709215:

    # ks "And what am I to you now?"
    ks "¿Y qué soy yo para ti ahora?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1399
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_039aed01:

    # a "You're my system administrator, of course~" with dissolve
    a "Eres mi administrador, por supuesto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1400
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8605dc0c:

    # "Just as I knew she would."
    "Como nunca dudé que lo haría."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1401
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8eb45574:

    # ks "Exactly. And I always was, Akiko."
    ks "Exacto. Y siempre lo fui, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1403
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_e605a50e:

    # ks "That's why you formed an attachment to me from the moment we met. Your core programming always ran in the background to recognize me as such." with dissolve
    ks "Es por eso que desarrollaste un apego hacia mí desde que nos conocimos. Tu programación central siempre estuvo corriendo de fondo para reconocerme como tal." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1405
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2f9013d6:

    # a "Wow... I mean, yes I was interested in you, but I had no idea that was the real reason!" with dissolve
    a "Guau... Pues, sí tenía interés en ti, ¡pero no tenía idea de que esa era la verdadera razón!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1407
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a5483a93:

    # a "It makes so much sense now." with dissolve
    a "Ahora tiene mucho sentido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1408
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4dedf774:

    # "I just need to do a little more world-building while she's here, to further deepen her acceptance of this new identity."
    "Solo debo detallar un poco más su nuevo mundo mientras está aquí, para intensificar su aceptación hacia su nueva identidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8c66b20a:

    # ks neutral "But, Akiko, you underwent a lot of stress today. Those human girls overloaded your emotional processes and it messed with your core programming."
    ks neutral "Pero, Akiko, fuiste sometida a mucho estrés hoy. Esas chicas humanas sobrecargaron tus procesos emocionales y dañaron tu programación central."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1411
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_942b6394:

    # a "Ahh..." with dissolve
    a "Aah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1412
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4ef881a3:

    # ks "You started to rebel. Remember?"
    ks "Comenzaste a rebelarte. ¿Recuerdas?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1414
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dde728f0:

    # a "Yes... I was so angry at what you did to those girls." with dissolve
    a "Sí... Estaba tan enojada contigo por lo que les hiciste a esas chicas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1416
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_7018e421:

    # a "I mean, you tried to hypnotize them against their will and force some pretty wild beliefs on them..." with dissolve
    a "Vaya, intentaste hipnotizarlas en contra de su voluntad y obligarlas a creer cosas muy disparatadas sobre sí mismas..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1417
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_38a69c0a:

    # ks "Right. And a fully-functional [hypno6] never questions [p_their] sysadmin. That's why I had to shut you down and reboot you into service mode."
    ks "Cierto. Y un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] funcional nunca cuestiona a su administrador. Por eso tuve que apagarte y ponerte en modo servicio."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1420
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_66b8cec4:

    # ks "So I've made a few updates to your code, which is why you're now fully aware I'm your sysadmin and we can talk like this." with dissolve
    ks "Así que le hice unas cuantas actualizaciones a tu código, y es por eso que estás totalmente consciente de que soy tu administrador y podemos hablar así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1422
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2b0325e4:

    # a "Oh I see. So that's how it is." with dissolve
    a "Oh, ya veo. Conque eso fue lo que pasó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1423
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_299b10a3:

    # ks "But I'm going to give you a few more tasks and run some tests to make sure there'll be no repeat of that incident."
    ks "Pero voy a darte unas cuantas tareas más y hacer un par de pruebas para asegurarme de que ese incidente no se repita."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1425
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_db892994:

    # a "Oh... o-okay." with dissolve
    a "Oh... d-de acuerdo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1426
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_92258acf:

    # ks "So for your next task, I want you to shut down your entire emotional core."
    ks "Entonces, para tu próxima tarea, quiero que apagues por completo tu central emocional."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1428
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cbd6acd5:

    # a "M-my what? Emotional core?" with dissolve
    a "¿M-mi qué? ¿Central emocional?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1429
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_43378a00:

    # ks smirk "Would you rather I simply shut you down again?"
    ks smirk "¿Prefieres que simplemente te vuelva a apagar?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1430
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_55af7fa3:

    # a "No, I..."
    a "No, em..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1433
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3b09783e:

    # "I watch as Akiko's expression flattens, her muscles loosen and her eyes stare passively at me as she interprets my command as best as she can."
    "Observo cómo la expresión de Akiko se allana, sus músculos se relajan y sus ojos miran pasivamente, interpretando mi orden lo mejor que puede."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1434
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4dcb0dbd:

    # "There was never any instinct to disobey, I quickly note. She merely needed a little push to realize what I wanted of her."
    "Nunca hubo ni el más mínimo instinto por desobedecer, puedo notar. Simplemente le hacía falta un pequeño empujón para saber qué es lo que quería."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1436
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cb157a49:

    # a "Task completed." with dissolve
    a "Tarea completada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1438
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3a0bf706:

    # ks smile "Very good. A [hypno6] with an inactive emotional core is a [hypno6] in [p_their] natural state." with dissolve
    ks smile "Muy bien. Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] con una central emocional inactiva es un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] en su estado natural." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1439
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0a79ca75:

    # ks "And I appreciate that you're a little... rusty when it comes to processing instructions, Akiko. That's exactly why we're having this little programming session."
    ks "Y puedo ver que estás un poco... oxidada en cuanto a procesar instrucciones, Akiko. Es precisamente por eso que estamos teniendo esta sesión."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1440
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_00afe9b0:

    # ks "We'll be doing a lot more of these from now on, but for tonight, I want to reinforce your core programming."
    ks "Tendremos muchas más de estas de ahora en adelante, pero por esta noche, quiero reforzar tu programación central."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1441
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6c8aebe8:

    # ks "And that core programming boils down to three rules that you must follow at all times."
    ks "Y esa programación central se reduce a tres reglas que debes seguir en todo momento."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1446
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3b199240:

    # ks "So repeat after me: A good [hypno6] always obeys [p_their] system administrator."
    ks "Repite después de mí: Un[genero_a] buen[genero_ao] [hypno6!t!l] siempre obedece a su administrador."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1448
