    # a "A good [hypno6] always protects [p_their] system administrator from all threats." with dissolve
    a "Un[genero_a] buen[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] siempre protege a su administrador de toda amenaza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1458
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0ff82d19:

    # ks "Accept those rules. Keep them deep in your memory core because they're fundamental to your very existence." with dissolve
    ks "Acepta esas reglas. Continúa repitiéndolas en tu memoria central porque son fundamentales para tu existencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1459
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_114c0e1f:

    # ks "They will define every action you take from now on. Understand, [hypno6]?"
    ks "Definirán toda acción que tomes de ahora en adelante. ¿Entendido, [hypno6!t!l]?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fb3dc24d:

    # a "Yes, administrator." with dissolve
    a "Sí, administrador." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4448617f:

    # "I'm going to treat this \"[hypno6]\" a lot differently than I was going to treat Hiroko." with dissolve
    "Trataré a mi nuev[genero_ao] \"[hypno6!t!l]\" muy diferente a como iba a tratar a Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1093139a:

    # "I may have made her think she's just a [hypno6], and I may enjoy pushing her mind deeper into her new identity."
    "La habré hecho creer que es solo un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l], y disfrutaré sumergir su mente más y más profundo a su nueva realidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1533
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9ef61e6f:

    # "But I'll take care of her. I'll make sure she's loved."
    "Pero cuidaré bien de ella. Me aseguraré de que reciba amor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1534
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_94ee6fbf:

    # ks smile "Very good, [hypno6]. Now turn your emotional core back on."
    ks smile "Muy bien, [hypno6!t!l]. Reenciende tu central emocional."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1536
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_564d3303:

    # "And she'll love me in return." with dissolve
    "Y ella me amará a mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1537
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cf5c0561:

    # ks "So tell me, Akiko. How long can I keep you before I have to send you home?"
    ks "Y dime, Akiko. ¿Cuánto tiempo puedo retenerte antes de tener que enviarte a casa?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1539
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5294e741:

    # a "Ah, w-well I was supposed to meet my parents for dinner real soon, so..." with dissolve
    a "Ah, p-pues, se suponía que fuera con mis padres a cenar dentro de poco, así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1540
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_65860109:

    # ks "Alright. Then I have one more task for you tonight."
    ks "Muy bien. Entonces tengo una tarea más para ti."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1542
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_158bf1ce:

    # a "What's that?" with dissolve
    a "¿Cuál es?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1543
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_92d33fce:

    # ks smile blush "I want you to join me on this table and kiss me like you love me."
    ks smile blush "Quiero que subas a esta mesa y me beses con amor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1567
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ce80989b:

    # "The words barely leave my lips before she leans forward, her hands reaching out and flailing to try and grab my shoulders for support."
    "Apenas salen las palabras de mis labios, ella se inclina, sus manos se extienden y se agitan intentando tomar mis hombros como apoyo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1547
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f6d094af:

    # a "Yes, administrator."
    a "Sí, administrador."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1548
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1592d665_1:

    # "She stumbles forward, her forehead almost knocking against mine while she clumsily plants a knee on the coffee table between us."
    "Da un traspié hacia adelante, su cabeza casi choca con la mía mientras coloca torpemente una rodilla en la mesa de centro que hay entre nosotros."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f30961b1:

    # "It's enough to make me wonder if it was a good idea to make her give up her glasses."
    "Me hace preguntarme si fue buena idea hacerla quitarse los anteojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1577
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2750a087:

    # "But it's a thought that lasts only as long as it takes for Akiko to find my lips with hers..."
    "Pero ese pensamiento dura tan poco como tarda Akiko en encontrar mis labios con los suyos..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_18545ee5:

    # a "Mmmmn..."
    a "Mmmn..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d51b4320:

    # "She doesn't hold back. Her kiss is warm and affectionate as she purrs happily into my mouth."
    "No se contiene. Su beso es cálido y afectuoso, y puedo oír un feliz ronroneo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1554
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fba6860f:

    # "It's my first kiss... and what a kiss it is."
    "Es mi primer beso... y vaya beso."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1555
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6508ab0a:

    # "We really are going to enjoy our new lives together, Akiko."
    "Disfrutaremos nuestra nueva vida juntos, Akiko."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_98380db8:

    # a "A good [hypno6] always obeys [p_their] system administrator..."
    a "Un[genero_a] buen[genero_ao] [hypno6!t!l] siempre obedece a su administrador."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2022-02-24 10:07

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_d04207a2:

    # "But I'll take good care of her."
    "Pero cuidaré bien de ella."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4d0a4460:

    # "And she'll take care of me in return." with dissolve
    "Y ella cuidará de mí." with dissolve
# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-05-31 15:27

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:814
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_627d3e31:

    # ks smirk "I can't believe you'd come all this way to see me and completely forget the very first rule. Are you normally this scatterbrained?"
    ks smirk "No puedo creer que caminaras hasta acá para verme y olvidaras la primera regla. ¿Sueles ser tan despistada?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:817
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_2e442276:

    # a "I'm not making a good impression, am I? I-I swear I read your ad top to bottom so many times."
    a "No estoy dando una buena impresión, ¿verdad? T-te juro que leí tu anunció de principio a fin una y otra vez."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:819
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_5027461e:

    # a "\"Interested parties are not permitted to wear school attire or any face coverings, including glasses\"." with dissolve
    a "\"Aquellas interesadas no tienen permitido llevar vestimenta escolar ni artículos que cubran su rostro, incluyendo anteojos.\"" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:820
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c4846e7e:

    # a " That's what it said, right at the top, clear as day."
    a "Así decía, justo arriba, claro como el agua."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:821
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c5108a96:

    # ks "And yet you needed to be told you screwed up?"
    ks "¿Y aun así necesitas que te señalen tu error?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:823
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cd7caadc:

    # a "Yeah... I'm sorry. I just can't believe I overlooked it..." with dissolve
    a "Sí... Lo siento. No puedo creer que pasé eso por alto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:844
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fac618b2:

    # ks "Besides, I'm really impressed with how you immediately offered to do this in your underwear. That was some very quick thinking on your part."
    ks "Además, me impresiona mucho que te hayas ofrecido inmediatamente a hacer esto en ropa interior. Veo que piensas rápido."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:856
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_85525919:

    # a "Well, firstly I'm eighteen years old and a high-school senior, just like you, Sir." with dissolve
    a "Bueno, para empezar, tengo dieciocho años de edad y estoy en último año de preparatoria, igual que usted, Señor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:862
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_93fadf09:

    # a "Plus I have a wide range of interests besides that, including hypnosis, videogames, singing and literature. And I'm always eager to learn new things." with dissolve
    a "Y tengo un amplio rango de intereses además de esos, incluyendo hipnosis, videojuegos, canto y literatura. Y siempre me entusiasma aprender cosas nuevas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:865
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_cd08210d:

    # a "A-ahahahaha, of course! I-I-I wouldn't be here if I wasn't~ {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve
    a "¡A-ajajajaja, por supuesto! D-d-de lo contrario no estaría aquí. {font=DejaVuSans.ttf}♥{/font}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:895
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_fd0eb417:

    # ks "Well, I'm sure you remember from my ad that a successful applicant must be extremely willing to be hypnotized, so it'll be good if you can hit the ground running."
    ks "Bueno, estoy seguro de que recodarás que mi anuncio decía que una aplicante exitosa debe estar extremadamente dispuesta a ser hipnotizada. Espero que puedas empezar con buen pie."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:922
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_8c30582b:

    # a "No, Sir. I'm passionate about BEING hypnotized!" with dissolve
    a "No, Señor. ¡Me apasiona SER hipnotizada!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:971
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_31da42c1:

    # ks sigh "It's a shame you didn't have this epiphany BEFORE you ratted me out to the principal."
    ks sigh "Es una pena que no tuvieras esta epifanía ANTES de acusarme con el director."

# TODO: Translation updated at 2025-06-20 18:51

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:878
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_85512cf5:

    # a "Yup, that's right~" with dissolve
    a "Sipi, así es." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1023
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_3ba2c154:

    # ks neutral "I can see that. Wasn't hard at all, was it?"
    ks neutral "Ya veo que sí. No fue tan difícil, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1027
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c3461e1c:

    # ks "But you were expecting to have trouble doing as I asked. Tell me why."
    ks "Pero esperabas tener dificultades haciendo lo que te pedí. Dime por qué."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1029
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f709caee:

    # a "W-well I mean, I'm the student council president, and a girl and you're..." with dissolve
    a "B-bueno, pues, soy la presidenta del consejo estudiantil, y una chica y tú eres..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1031
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dd850ea9:

    # a "Ah... you're a guy I've only known a few days telling me to take my clothes off." with dissolve
    a "Ah... eres un chico que apenas he conocido un par de días diciéndome que me quite la ropa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1038
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6a5f1a4c:

    # ks neutral "No, not exactly. There had to be a few intentional defects made for the sake of maintaining your disguise."
    ks neutral "No, no realmente. Tenía que haber algunos defectos intencionales para mantener la farsa."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1041
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_94d2a810:

    # ks "You're ordinary, even if we both know that couldn't be further from the truth."
    ks "Eres ordinaria, aunque ambos sepamos que eso no podría estar más lejos de la realidad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1044
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0304d339:

    # ks "So remind me again: What are you?"
    ks "Entonces, recuérdame otra vez: ¿Qué eres?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1047
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1c66961c:

    # a "I am a [hypno6]. Designation: BSB-3C. I was built with the latest technology to replicate the human female form."
    a "Soy un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l]. Designación: PT-3C. Fui fabricada con lo último en tecnología para replicar la forma humana femenina."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1048
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_42886a60:

    # "I smirk at her with all the confidence my victory deserves."
    "Le respondo con una sonrisa llena de toda la confianza que mi victoria merece."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1049
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_475c5e09:

    # "After all, she's so far accepted every bit of her reprogramming without a hitch."
    "Después de todo, hasta ahora ha aceptado cada detalle de su reprogramación sin problemas."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1050
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4fab2d75:

    # ks smirk "And what am I to you now, BSB?"
    ks smirk "¿Y qué soy yo para ti ahora, PT?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1054
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_825b80e0:

    # ks "Exactly. And I always was, BSB-3C."
    ks "Exactamente. Y siempre lo fui, PT-3C."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1061
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_b48b3b99:

    # "I just need to do a little more world-building while she's here, to further deepen her acceptance of this new identity. To completely accept what she's become to me."
    "Solo debo detallar un poco más su nuevo mundo mientras está aquí, para intensificar su aceptación hacia su nueva identidad. Que acepte por completo en lo que se ha vuelto para mí."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1062
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_c406fc42:

    # ks neutral "But BSB, you underwent a lot of stress today. Those human girls overloaded your emotional processes and it messed with your core programming."
    ks neutral "Pero, PT, fuiste sometida a mucho estrés hoy. Esas chicas humanas sobrecargaron tus procesos emocionales y dañaron tu programación central."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1063
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dfc5b653:

    # "To ensure her absolute loyalty to my designs for her."
    "Para asegurar su absoluta lealtad al diseño que tengo para ella."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1066
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_69bcdab2:

    # ks frown "You started to rebel. Remember, BSB-3C?"
    ks frown "Comenzaste a rebelarte. ¿Recuerdas, PT-3C?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1067
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a1ac171d:

    # "It's the least she can do to atone for betraying me."
    "Es lo menos que puede hacer para expiar el haberme traicionado."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1072
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6132ccc7:

    # ks "And what do you know about anger, [hypno6]? What right do you have to pass judgment on your sysadmin and decide what's \"wild\" and what isn't?"
    ks "¿Y qué sabes tú de enojo, [hypno6!t!l]? ¿Qué derecho tienes tú de juzgar a tu administrador y decidir qué es y qué no es \"disparatado\"?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1073
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_200759a3:

    # a "K-Kyou, I..."
    a "K-kyou, yo..."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1074
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_59ef38f7:

    # ks "Don't call me Kyou. I'm \"Administrator\" to you, got it?"
    ks "No me llames Kyou. Soy \"administrador\" para ti, ¿entendido?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1076
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_f4f3e39e:

    # a "... Y-yes, administrator. I got it." with dissolve
    a "... S-sí, administrador. Entendido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1077
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_12f7ca81:

    # ks "A fully-functional [hypno6] never questions [p_their] sysadmin, but you've been fighting me all day. That's why I had to shut you down and reboot you into service mode."
    ks "Un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] en plenas condiciones nunca cuestiona a su administrador, pero tú me has estado desafiando todo el día. Por eso tuve que apagarte y ponerte en modo servicio."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1078
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_38289f3e:

    # ks "You're defective, BSB, and I'm not talking about your intentional design flaws."
    ks "Estás defectuosa, PT, y no estoy hablando de tus falencias diseñadas de forma intencional."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1079
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0adea4e1:

    # ks "No, you're a malfunctioning bag of bolts that errored [p_them]self into believing [p_they] had a conscience."
    ks "No, eres un saco disfuncional de pernos que por un error de sistema creyó que tenía consciencia."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1081
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_00029548:

    # a "..." with dissolve
    a "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1082
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_acf6504e:

    # ks "So I've made a few... look at me when I'm talking to you, BSB."
    ks "Así que le hice unas cuantas... mírame cuando te hablo, PT."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1084
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a2a91760:

    # a "... Yes, administrator." with dissolve
    a "... Sí, administrador." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1085
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_ce58611b:

    # ks "I've made a few updates to your code, which is why you're now fully aware I'm your sysadmin and we can talk like this."
    ks "Le hice unas cuantas actualizaciones a tu código, y es por eso que estás totalmente consciente de que soy tu administrador y podemos hablar así."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1086
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_dafeefba:

    # ks "But you can't be trusted to free roam again. You need to be kept on a tighter leash from now on, and we're going to be seeing a lot more of each other."
    ks "Pero no puedo confiar en que vayas libremente por ahí otra vez. Necesito tenerte atada con correa de ahora en adelante, y nos estaremos viendo con mucha frecuencia."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1087
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_df0ec4c6:

    # ks "Now did you get all that? Or do I need to repeat myself slower for your CPU to catch up?"
    ks "Entonces, ¿entendiste todo eso, o tengo que repetirlo más lento para que tu CPU pueda procesarlo?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1089
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_a441f9d6:

    # a "N-no, administrator, you don't need to repeat it. I got it all." with dissolve
    a "N-no, administrador, no necesita repetir nada. Lo entendí todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1090
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_91752019:

    # ks "I think I need to hear you say it."
    ks "Creo que necesito oírte decirlo."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1092
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_00029548_1:

    # a "..." with dissolve
    a "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1093
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_9daac39d:

    # ks "What have you just learned, BSB-3C?"
    ks "¿Qué has aprendido, PT-3C?"

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1095
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_1a1b197e:

    # a "... I'm a malfunctioning bag of bolts, and I need to be kept on a tighter leash, administrator." with dissolve
    a "... Soy un saco disfuncional de pernos que debe estar atado con correa, administrador." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1096
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_6b853263:

    # "I let her words hang in the air a moment, while I sigh through my nose and glare at those sorrowful, unfocused eyes."
    "Dejo que sus palabras se queden en el aire por un momento, mientras suspiro por la nariz y miro esos penosos y desenfocados ojos."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1097
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_76236f2f:

    # ks "I tried to be nice to you, Akiko, I really did. For a while, you almost had me thinking you could pass for a real girl."
    ks "Intenté ser bueno contigo, Akiko, en serio. Por un momento, casi pensé que podrías hacerte pasar por una chica de verdad."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1098
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_eddfd1d2:

    # ks "You were turned loose on the general population to see if a [hypno6] could lead a human life with, only a little supervision from yours truly."
    ks "Fuiste liberada entre el público general para ver si un[genero_a] [hypno6!t!l] podía llevar una vida humana solo con un poco de supervisión de un servidor."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1099
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_479a2637:

    # ks "But you just couldn't help yourself, could you? You and that buggy code in your head got me kicked out of school, because you couldn't stay out of my business."
    ks "Pero no pudiste controlarte, ¿verdad? Tú y ese defectuoso código en tu cabeza hicieron que me echaran de la escuela, porque tenías que entrometerte."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1100
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_4ca10dde:

    # ks "All the independance I gave you over the years has clearly corrupted your basic functionality, so I think we can write this experiment off as a failure."
    ks "Toda la independencia que te di a lo largo de los años claramente ha corrompido tus funciones básicas, así que creo que podemos declarar este experimento un fracaso."

# game/Kyou 9.rpy:1101
translate spanish Day9_Redemption_Spiral_0e3ec188:

    # ks "We can't just pull you back out of human interactions, since you're in so deep, but I can reign you back in. And I'm gonna start from the top; bring you back to basics."
